WEBVTT

00:00:08.470 --> 00:00:10.272
[<i>Uragiri no Yuyake</i>

00:00:10.272 --> 00:00:11.839
by Theater Brook]

00:00:11.839 --> 00:00:14.842
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:00:14.842 --> 00:00:22.885
♪ ♪

00:01:14.106 --> 00:01:15.852
&gt;&gt; I’LL RELY ON NUMBERS!

00:01:15.852 --> 00:01:17.519
&gt;&gt; both: IT’S HERE!

00:01:17.519 --> 00:01:19.255
&gt;&gt; THIS IS THE DOLLARS?

00:01:19.255 --> 00:01:20.222
&gt;&gt; WHAT IS THIS?

00:01:20.222 --> 00:01:20.790
THEY CAN’T--

00:01:20.790 --> 00:01:22.291
ARE THEY ALL REALLY--

00:01:22.291 --> 00:01:24.226
&gt;&gt; FOR STARTERS, YOU COULD MARRY

00:01:24.226 --> 00:01:24.727
ME.

00:01:24.727 --> 00:01:26.295
&gt;&gt; AFTER ALL, YOU ARE KEEPING

00:01:26.295 --> 00:01:28.230
THAT THING A SECRET.

00:01:28.230 --> 00:01:28.965
&gt;&gt; CELTY.

00:01:28.965 --> 00:01:30.199
&gt;&gt; [chuckles]

00:01:30.199 --> 00:01:31.634
THIS IS SO MUCH FUN.

00:01:31.634 --> 00:01:32.902
&gt;&gt; DO YOU HEAR ME SCREAMING?

00:01:32.902 --> 00:01:34.437
THIS IS MY MOMENT.

00:01:34.437 --> 00:01:36.339
THIS IS MY TIME TO BE BORN.

00:01:36.339 --> 00:01:37.540
&gt;&gt; I WANT CELTY.

00:01:37.540 --> 00:01:38.708
GIVE HER BACK!

00:01:38.708 --> 00:01:41.711
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:01:41.711 --> 00:01:49.753
♪ ♪

00:02:05.236 --> 00:02:07.805
[running]

00:02:07.805 --> 00:02:13.778
[grunting]

00:02:13.778 --> 00:02:15.313
&gt;&gt; I HAVE TO THANK YOU FOR WHAT

00:02:15.313 --> 00:02:16.247
YOU’VE DONE.

00:02:16.247 --> 00:02:17.515
IF IT WEREN’T FOR YOU, I’M

00:02:17.515 --> 00:02:18.750
PRETTY SURE MY SISTER WOULD

00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:19.684
HAVE JUST LOCKED HER IN THAT

00:02:19.684 --> 00:02:21.586
CRAMPED RESEARCH LAB AGAIN.

00:02:21.586 --> 00:02:25.657
&gt;&gt; SEIJI.

00:02:25.657 --> 00:02:26.791
YOU OKAY?

00:02:26.791 --> 00:02:27.759
&gt;&gt; I WANT YOU TO GIVE CELTY

00:02:27.759 --> 00:02:28.593
BACK.

00:02:28.593 --> 00:02:29.628
SHE AND I HAVE TO GET OUT OF

00:02:29.628 --> 00:02:31.463
HERE BEFORE THE COPS ARRIVE.

00:02:31.463 --> 00:02:32.964
&gt;&gt; YOU THINK THIS’LL WORK?

00:02:32.964 --> 00:02:33.632
IT WON’T!

00:02:33.632 --> 00:02:34.666
&gt;&gt; YOU DON’T KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT

00:02:34.666 --> 00:02:35.600
THIS.

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:36.768
I’VE BEEN WATCHING AND ADMIRING

00:02:36.768 --> 00:02:38.037
HER EVER SINCE I WAS A LITTLE

00:02:38.037 --> 00:02:39.772
KID.

00:02:39.772 --> 00:02:41.707
I WANTED TO SET HER FREE.

00:02:41.707 --> 00:02:42.775
RELEASE HER INTO THIS GREAT BIG

00:02:42.775 --> 00:02:44.543
WORLD WHERE THE TWO OF US WOULD

00:02:44.543 --> 00:02:46.646
LIVE TOGETHER FOREVER.

00:02:46.646 --> 00:02:48.614
SHE’S ALL I EVER THINK ABOUT.

00:02:48.614 --> 00:02:50.315
EVERY DAY, EVERY HOUR, EVERY

00:02:50.315 --> 00:02:52.685
MINUTE.

00:02:52.685 --> 00:02:53.686
WHAT CAN I SAY?

00:02:53.686 --> 00:02:55.521
NO ONE CAN STOP THE POWER OF

00:02:55.521 --> 00:02:56.422
LOVE.

00:02:56.422 --> 00:02:57.757
BUT ENOUGH ABOUT ME.

00:02:57.757 --> 00:02:59.024
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

00:02:59.024 --> 00:03:00.660
SEEMS LIKE YOU KEEP RELYING ON

00:03:00.660 --> 00:03:03.463
NUMBERS TO HELP YOU OUT.

00:03:03.463 --> 00:03:03.930
[grunts]

00:03:03.930 --> 00:03:05.498
[exclamations]

00:03:05.498 --> 00:03:06.666
IT’LL TAKE MORE THAN THAT TO

00:03:06.666 --> 00:03:08.401
STOP OUR LOVE!

00:03:08.401 --> 00:03:10.671
[grunting]

00:03:10.671 --> 00:03:11.738
IT’S NO USE!

00:03:11.738 --> 00:03:13.607
PAIN MEANS NOTHING TO ME.

00:03:13.607 --> 00:03:14.708
THERE’LL BE NO PAIN IN THE LIFE

00:03:14.708 --> 00:03:16.076
I’LL HAVE WITH CELTY.

00:03:16.076 --> 00:03:17.611
BEAT ME ALL YOU WANT, I DON’T

00:03:17.611 --> 00:03:18.311
CARE.

00:03:18.311 --> 00:03:19.580
I WON’T FEEL IT!

00:03:19.580 --> 00:03:21.848
&gt;&gt; THAT’S INSANE!

00:03:29.590 --> 00:03:31.993
&gt;&gt; NO, DON’T!

00:03:34.395 --> 00:03:35.730
PLEASE DON’T HURT HIM!

00:03:35.730 --> 00:03:36.831
JUST LISTEN.

00:03:36.831 --> 00:03:37.965
I KNOW SEIJI IS HARSH AND

00:03:37.965 --> 00:03:39.400
VIOLENT AT TIMES BUT HE’S NOT A

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:40.568
BAD PERSON.

00:03:40.568 --> 00:03:41.536
AND THERE’S SOMEONE IN THIS

00:03:41.536 --> 00:03:43.638
WORLD HE TRULY LOVES.

00:03:43.638 --> 00:03:45.372
&gt;&gt; NO WAY.

00:03:45.372 --> 00:03:47.475
NO, THIS CAN’T BE.

00:03:47.475 --> 00:03:48.009
THIS CAN’T BE!

00:03:48.009 --> 00:03:52.046
&gt;&gt; I DON’T BELIEVE IT. THAT’S...

00:03:52.046 --> 00:03:54.482
&gt;&gt; THAT ISN’T MY HEAD!

00:03:54.482 --> 00:03:55.783
&gt;&gt; THAT GIRL.

00:03:55.783 --> 00:03:57.953
IS HER NAME...

00:03:57.953 --> 00:04:00.889
MIKA HARIMA.

00:04:00.889 --> 00:04:02.457
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE HER, AREN’T YOU?

00:04:02.457 --> 00:04:04.126
THE GIRL THAT SEIJI SUPPOSEDLY

00:04:04.126 --> 00:04:05.493
KILLED.

00:04:05.493 --> 00:04:09.097
YOU’RE MIKA HARIMA!

00:04:09.097 --> 00:04:11.767
&gt;&gt; CAN’T BE.

00:04:11.767 --> 00:04:13.869
TELL ME...

00:04:13.869 --> 00:04:15.704
HE’S WRONG.

00:04:15.704 --> 00:04:17.506
&gt;&gt; I’M SO SORRY!

00:04:17.506 --> 00:04:18.707
HELLO, SEIJI.

00:04:18.707 --> 00:04:20.409
I KNOW THAT YOU’RE IN THERE.

00:04:20.409 --> 00:04:21.810
I’VE COME BACK AGAIN!

00:04:21.810 --> 00:04:23.112
OH, NO, YOU FORGOT TO LEAVE THE

00:04:23.112 --> 00:04:24.780
DOOR OPEN FOR ME.

00:04:24.780 --> 00:04:26.415
I CAN’T COME IN AND SEE YOU.

00:04:26.415 --> 00:04:28.818
ARE YOU SLEEPING RIGHT NOW?

00:04:28.818 --> 00:04:30.386
O YOU REMEMBER ME?

00:04:30.386 --> 00:04:31.554
I’M THE GIRL WHO SAT NEXT TO

00:04:31.554 --> 00:04:32.989
YOU DURING THE ENTRANCE EXAM AT

00:04:32.989 --> 00:04:34.590
SCHOOL.

00:04:34.590 --> 00:04:36.025
TO MY RIGHT WAS SOME KID WITH A

00:04:36.025 --> 00:04:38.662
WEIRD LAST NAME LIKE RYUGAMINE.

00:04:38.662 --> 00:04:39.896
SO I TURNED TO MY LEFT TO SEE

00:04:39.896 --> 00:04:40.897
WHAT THAT PERSON’S LAST NAME

00:04:40.897 --> 00:04:41.831
WAS...

00:04:41.831 --> 00:04:42.899
AND FELL IN LOVE THE MOMENT I

00:04:42.899 --> 00:04:43.900
SAW YOU.

00:04:43.900 --> 00:04:45.902
WHEN OUR EYES MET, YOU SMILED

00:04:45.902 --> 00:04:49.173
AT ME.

00:04:49.173 --> 00:04:50.140
COME ON, SEIJI.

00:04:50.140 --> 00:04:51.875
SHOW ME YOUR FACE AGAIN!

00:04:51.875 --> 00:04:53.010
PLEASE, PLEASE!

00:04:53.010 --> 00:04:54.644
MAYBE YOU’RE NOT FEELING GOOD.

00:04:54.644 --> 00:04:55.579
IS THAT WHY YOU CAN’T ANSWER

00:04:55.579 --> 00:04:56.080
THE DOOR?

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:57.747
IF THAT’S THE CASE, THEN DON’T

00:04:57.747 --> 00:04:58.582
WORRY ABOUT IT.

00:04:58.582 --> 00:04:59.784
I’ll OPEN IT....

00:04:59.784 --> 00:05:01.118
RIGHT NOW!

00:05:01.118 --> 00:05:03.120
[door unlocks]

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:04.789
AFTER WE MET TAKING THE EXAM,

00:05:04.789 --> 00:05:06.657
I DID A LITTLE RESEARCH.

00:05:06.657 --> 00:05:08.058
I KNOW YOUR BIRTHDAY AND YOUR

00:05:08.058 --> 00:05:09.894
FAMILY...

00:05:19.904 --> 00:05:23.774
S-SEIJI?

00:05:23.774 --> 00:05:24.943
&gt;&gt; YOU SAW IT?

00:05:24.943 --> 00:05:26.845
&gt;&gt; YEAH, BUT IT’S OKAY.

00:05:26.845 --> 00:05:29.180
I WON’T TELL ANYONE, I PROMISE.

00:05:29.180 --> 00:05:32.083
I-I WON’T TELL A SOUL!

00:05:32.083 --> 00:05:33.752
WHATEVER YOU’RE INTO, IT’S FINE.

00:05:33.752 --> 00:05:34.820
I’M COOL WITH IT!

00:05:34.820 --> 00:05:36.788
UM, SO I...

00:05:36.788 --> 00:05:37.723
&gt;&gt; IT’S OKAY.

00:05:37.723 --> 00:05:39.858
&gt;&gt; SEIJI!

00:05:39.858 --> 00:05:41.527
&gt;&gt; IT’S OKAY.

00:05:41.527 --> 00:05:43.929
&gt;&gt; SEIJI, ARE YOU...

00:05:43.929 --> 00:05:46.798
&gt;&gt; IT’S OKAY.

00:05:46.798 --> 00:05:48.834
[grunts]

00:05:48.834 --> 00:05:49.868
&gt;&gt; I’M SORRY!

00:05:49.868 --> 00:05:51.971
I’M SORRY I DIDN’T DIE!

00:05:51.971 --> 00:05:55.241
AND THEN YOUR SISTER...

00:05:55.241 --> 00:05:56.743
&gt;&gt; YOU WANT SEIJI TO LOVE YOU,

00:05:56.743 --> 00:05:59.979
RIGHT?

00:05:59.979 --> 00:06:00.980
GOOD GIRL.

00:06:00.980 --> 00:06:02.482
AND THAT’S WHEN THIS DOCTOR

00:06:02.482 --> 00:06:03.850
SHOWED UP.

00:06:03.850 --> 00:06:04.984
HE SAID THAT, WITH A LITTLE

00:06:04.984 --> 00:06:06.586
PLASTIC SURGERY AND SOME MAKEUP,

00:06:06.586 --> 00:06:08.154
I COULD LOOK JUST LIKE THE HEAD

00:06:08.154 --> 00:06:09.989
THAT YOU’RE IN LOVE WITH.

00:06:09.989 --> 00:06:11.123
HE TOLD ME MY NAME WOULD BE

00:06:11.123 --> 00:06:11.991
CELTY.

00:06:11.991 --> 00:06:13.493
BECAUSE THAT’S WHAT THE HEAD IS

00:06:13.493 --> 00:06:14.127
CALLED.

00:06:14.127 --> 00:06:15.895
I TRIED, I TRIED HARD TO BE

00:06:15.895 --> 00:06:17.830
CELTY FOR YOUR SAKE.

00:06:17.830 --> 00:06:18.999
BUT YOUR SISTER SAID IT WASN’T

00:06:18.999 --> 00:06:20.233
ENOUGH.

00:06:20.233 --> 00:06:21.568
SHE WANTED ME TO START TAKING

00:06:21.568 --> 00:06:23.003
DRUGS AND HAVE MORE SURGERY TO

00:06:23.003 --> 00:06:24.905
ERASE MY MEMORIES.

00:06:24.905 --> 00:06:25.873
BUT I DIDN’T WANT TO DO THAT.

00:06:25.873 --> 00:06:28.075
&gt;&gt; A DOCTOR WHO KNOWS MY NAME...

00:06:28.075 --> 00:06:28.876
&gt;&gt; I LOVE YOU.

00:06:28.876 --> 00:06:30.110
&gt;&gt; WHO KNOWS THAT I’M A

00:06:30.110 --> 00:06:31.845
DULLAHAN.

00:06:31.845 --> 00:06:32.946
&gt;&gt; SO I RAN AWAY...

00:06:32.946 --> 00:06:33.947
&gt;&gt; THERE’S ONLY ONE PERSON LIKE

00:06:33.947 --> 00:06:36.650
THAT IN THIS WHOLE CITY!

00:06:36.650 --> 00:06:38.118
&gt;&gt; I DID ALL THIS FOR YOU!

00:06:38.118 --> 00:06:40.288
SO I COULD BE WITH YOU!

00:06:40.288 --> 00:06:41.889
[crowd murmuring]

00:06:41.889 --> 00:06:44.926
[horse whinnies]

00:06:44.926 --> 00:06:47.962
&gt;&gt; NO, THIS CAN’T BE TRUE.

00:06:47.962 --> 00:06:48.897
THIS MEANS THAT...

00:06:48.897 --> 00:06:50.198
&gt;&gt; WELL...YOU COULDN’T EVEN TELL

00:06:50.198 --> 00:06:51.132
THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN THE

00:06:51.132 --> 00:06:53.702
GENUINE ARTICLE AND THE FAKE.

00:06:53.702 --> 00:06:54.669
GUESS YOUR LOVE WASN’T THAT

00:06:54.669 --> 00:06:55.904
STRONG AFTER ALL.

00:06:55.904 --> 00:07:00.008
SUCKS TO BE YOU.

00:07:00.008 --> 00:07:02.544
&gt;&gt; SEIJI!

00:07:02.544 --> 00:07:04.012
&gt;&gt; UM, I HAVE TO SAY, THE FACT

00:07:04.012 --> 00:07:05.046
THAT YOU WERE WILLING TO RISK

00:07:05.046 --> 00:07:06.114
YOUR LIFE TO GET HER BACK IS

00:07:06.114 --> 00:07:07.249
PRETTY ADMIRABLE.

00:07:07.249 --> 00:07:08.717
AND IT TURNS OUT THAT I WAS

00:07:08.717 --> 00:07:11.053
ACTUALLY WRONG ABOUT MIKA.

00:07:11.053 --> 00:07:12.621
SOME OF THE THINGS SHE DOES MAY

00:07:12.621 --> 00:07:14.089
BE STRANGE BUT...I REALLY

00:07:14.089 --> 00:07:16.058
DON’T THINK SHE’S A STALKER.

00:07:16.058 --> 00:07:18.060
I MEAN, YOU RISKED YOUR LIFE TO

00:07:18.060 --> 00:07:19.161
SAVE SEIJI.

00:07:19.161 --> 00:07:20.195
I DON’T THINK SOMEONE WOULD DO

00:07:20.195 --> 00:07:21.664
THAT IF THEY WERE ONLY IN IT

00:07:21.664 --> 00:07:22.865
FOR THEMSELVES.

00:07:22.865 --> 00:07:24.033
AND EVEN THOUGH HE TRIED TO

00:07:24.033 --> 00:07:25.735
KILL YOU, YOU STILL LOVED HIM.

00:07:25.735 --> 00:07:27.069
THAT’S AMAZING.

00:07:27.069 --> 00:07:28.270
IN SOME WAYS.

00:07:28.270 --> 00:07:30.573
SO THEN I GUESS...YOU AND

00:07:30.573 --> 00:07:35.611
SEIJI...YOU’RE A LOT ALIKE.

00:07:35.611 --> 00:07:36.146
[door slams]

00:07:36.146 --> 00:07:38.014
[footsteps]

00:07:38.014 --> 00:07:38.881
[door opening and shutting]

00:07:38.881 --> 00:07:44.254
&gt;&gt; WELCOME HOME.

00:07:44.254 --> 00:07:45.355
I’M GUESSING YOU WANT TO KNOW

00:07:45.355 --> 00:07:48.024
WHY I DID WHAT I DID.

00:07:48.024 --> 00:07:50.226
AND YOUR NEXT QUESTION IS...

00:07:50.226 --> 00:07:51.662
"YOU’VE KNOWN ALL ALONG, HAVEN’T

00:07:51.662 --> 00:07:52.162
YOU?

00:07:52.162 --> 00:07:54.230
THAT MY HEAD WAS IN THEIR LAB?

00:07:54.230 --> 00:07:56.099
I BET YOU AND YOUR DAD HAD BEEN

00:07:56.099 --> 00:07:56.967
WORKING WITH YAGIRI

00:07:56.967 --> 00:07:58.969
PHARMACEUTICALS THIS WHOLE TIME.

00:07:58.969 --> 00:08:00.704
AND CHANCES ARE IT WAS YOUR DAD

00:08:00.704 --> 00:08:02.005
WHO TOOK MY HEAD FROM ME IN

00:08:02.005 --> 00:08:03.073
THE FIRST PLACE!

00:08:03.073 --> 00:08:04.208
BUT FOR SOME REASON YOU DECIDED

00:08:04.208 --> 00:08:05.976
TO HIDE ALL THAT FROM ME.

00:08:05.976 --> 00:08:07.211
AND BUTCHERED SOME POOR,

00:08:07.211 --> 00:08:09.113
INNOCENT GIRL’S FACE INSTEAD!

00:08:09.113 --> 00:08:10.814
I MAY BE A MONSTER...

00:08:10.814 --> 00:08:12.083
BUT THE SAVAGE BEAST WHO REALLY

00:08:12.083 --> 00:08:14.218
DESTROYS PEOPLE’S LIVES IS YOU!"

00:08:14.218 --> 00:08:15.753
WAS THAT CLOSE?

00:08:15.753 --> 00:08:17.354
LOOK, I JUST DON’T WANT THERE

00:08:17.354 --> 00:08:18.956
TO BE ANY CONFUSION ON THIS.

00:08:18.956 --> 00:08:20.057
I REALLY DON’T KNOW IF MY DAD

00:08:20.057 --> 00:08:21.626
STOLE YOUR HEAD OR NOT, AND, TO

00:08:21.626 --> 00:08:22.994
BE HONEST, I DON’T CARE.

00:08:22.994 --> 00:08:24.362
AND THAT POOR GIRL YOU SPOKE OF

00:08:24.362 --> 00:08:25.897
VOLUNTEERED FOR THAT SURGERY,

00:08:25.897 --> 00:08:28.366
ALTHOUGH CHANCES ARE YAGIRI DID

00:08:28.366 --> 00:08:30.768
PERSUADE HER TO DO IT.

00:08:30.768 --> 00:08:31.903
BUT IN THE END, THAT’S NONE OF

00:08:31.903 --> 00:08:34.072
MY BUSINESS.

00:08:34.072 --> 00:08:35.040
"DO YOU REALLY KNOW WHAT I’M

00:08:35.040 --> 00:08:36.041
THINKING?

00:08:36.041 --> 00:08:37.042
ARE YOU ACTUALLY READING MY

00:08:37.042 --> 00:08:38.977
MIND?" YOU ASK?

00:08:38.977 --> 00:08:41.113
YES...OF COURSE I CAN.

00:08:41.113 --> 00:08:42.715
I’VE LOVED YOU FOR TWENTY YEARS,

00:08:42.715 --> 00:08:43.281
CELTY.

00:08:43.281 --> 00:08:45.183
I CAN TELL WHAT YOU’RE THINKING.

00:08:45.183 --> 00:08:46.051
&gt;&gt; [gasps]

00:08:46.051 --> 00:08:47.285
&gt;&gt; BUT THEN WHY?

00:08:47.285 --> 00:08:48.887
IF YOU LOVE ME, WHY DIDN’T YOU

00:08:48.887 --> 00:08:51.724
TELL ME WHERE MY HEAD WAS?

00:08:51.724 --> 00:08:53.426
&gt;&gt; THAT’S THE REASON.

00:08:53.426 --> 00:08:55.027
IT’S BECAUSE I LOVE YOU THAT I

00:08:55.027 --> 00:08:55.961
DIDN’T TELL YOU.

00:08:55.961 --> 00:08:57.763
IF YOU HAD YOUR HEAD, THEN I’M

00:08:57.763 --> 00:08:59.298
AFRAID YOU WOULD LEAVE ME.

00:08:59.298 --> 00:09:00.333
AND I KNOW THAT I COULDN’T BEAR

00:09:00.333 --> 00:09:02.001
THAT.

00:09:02.001 --> 00:09:03.069
EVEN THOUGH I KNEW IT’D MAKE

00:09:03.069 --> 00:09:05.004
YOU HAPPY, I COULDN’T TELL YOU.

00:09:05.004 --> 00:09:06.205
WE’RE EACH FIGHTING FOR

00:09:06.205 --> 00:09:07.740
SOMETHING, AND WHAT’S AT STAKE

00:09:07.740 --> 00:09:08.875
ARE OUR HEARTS.

00:09:08.875 --> 00:09:10.376
I NEVER WANT TO LOSE YOU.

00:09:10.376 --> 00:09:11.678
AND IF I HAVE TO SACRIFICE THE

00:09:11.678 --> 00:09:13.212
LIFE AND LOVE OF OTHERS, OR

00:09:13.212 --> 00:09:15.882
EVEN MYSELF, THEN SO BE IT.

00:09:15.882 --> 00:09:17.050
IT’S HYPOCRITICAL...

00:09:17.050 --> 00:09:18.051
BUT IF I HAVE TO USE YOUR

00:09:18.051 --> 00:09:23.257
EMOTIONS TOO, I WILL.

00:09:23.257 --> 00:09:24.358
&gt;&gt; I DON’T KNOW WHY YOU’D THINK

00:09:24.358 --> 00:09:25.292
THAT.

00:09:25.292 --> 00:09:26.693
EVEN IF I HAD MY HEAD, I

00:09:26.693 --> 00:09:27.461
WOULDN’T LEAVE YOU.

00:09:27.461 --> 00:09:28.195
I...

00:09:28.195 --> 00:09:29.696
&gt;&gt; THAT MAY BE WHAT YOUR HEART

00:09:29.696 --> 00:09:31.465
WANTS, BUT...YOUR HEAD MAY NOT

00:09:31.465 --> 00:09:33.300
FEEL THE SAME.

00:09:33.300 --> 00:09:34.768
I’VE REALLY THOUGHT ABOUT THIS.

00:09:34.768 --> 00:09:36.470
YOU’RE A MYTHICAL FAERIE.

00:09:36.470 --> 00:09:37.738
WHY DO YOU CHOOSE TO REVEAL

00:09:37.738 --> 00:09:39.273
YOURSELF TO HUMANS AS EASILY AS

00:09:39.273 --> 00:09:40.975
YOU DO?

00:09:40.975 --> 00:09:42.176
MAYBE SOMEHOW BY LOSING YOUR

00:09:42.176 --> 00:09:44.011
HEAD, IT’S ALLOWED YOU TO TAKE

00:09:44.011 --> 00:09:46.080
ON MORE OF A PHYSICAL FORM.

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:48.248
AND IF THAT’S TRUE, THEN WHO’S

00:09:48.248 --> 00:09:49.784
TO SAY AFTER YOU GET YOUR HEAD

00:09:49.784 --> 00:09:51.118
BACK THAT YOU WON’T JUST VANISH

00:09:51.118 --> 00:09:53.321
INTO THIN AIR, AS IF ALL OF

00:09:53.321 --> 00:09:54.322
THIS WAS NOTHING MORE THAN A

00:09:54.322 --> 00:09:56.091
DREAM?

00:09:56.091 --> 00:09:58.159
THAT’S MY BIGGEST FEAR.

00:10:06.134 --> 00:10:07.402
&gt;&gt; WILL YOU BELIEVE WHAT I’M

00:10:07.402 --> 00:10:09.971
ABOUT TO SAY?

00:10:09.971 --> 00:10:11.172
&gt;&gt; IF YOU SAY IT’S TRUE, I’LL

00:10:11.172 --> 00:10:11.873
BELIEVE YOU.

00:10:11.873 --> 00:10:13.341
TO BE HONEST, YOU’RE THE ONLY

00:10:13.341 --> 00:10:15.243
ONE I BELIEVE.

00:10:15.243 --> 00:10:17.145
&gt;&gt; I’M SCARED TOO.

00:10:17.145 --> 00:10:20.182
I’M SCARED OF DYING.

00:10:20.182 --> 00:10:21.350
I KNOW THAT IN MY CURRENT

00:10:21.350 --> 00:10:22.484
PHYSICAL STATE, NO ONE’S

00:10:22.484 --> 00:10:25.221
CAPABLE OF KILLING ME.

00:10:25.221 --> 00:10:26.788
THIS ISN’T ME BEING ARROGANT.

00:10:26.788 --> 00:10:28.424
IT JUST A STATEMENT OF FACT.

00:10:28.424 --> 00:10:30.259
I TAKE NO JOY OR SATISFACTION

00:10:30.259 --> 00:10:31.227
FROM THIS.

00:10:31.227 --> 00:10:33.262
IT’S JUST TRUE.

00:10:33.262 --> 00:10:34.363
BUT, TO BE HONEST, THAT’S WHAT

00:10:34.363 --> 00:10:36.232
SCARES ME THE MOST.

