AND IF SOMEONE WERE TO DESTROY

00:10:44.907 --> 00:10:46.943
MY HEAD, THEN I WOULD DIE TOO,

00:10:46.943 --> 00:10:49.146
NO MATTER WHAT I WANT OR WHERE

00:10:49.146 --> 00:10:53.183
I AM!

00:10:53.183 --> 00:10:54.351
I NEED YOU TO BELIEVE WHAT I’M

00:10:54.351 --> 00:10:55.318
TELLING YOU.

00:10:55.318 --> 00:10:56.786
I MAY NOT HAVE A BRAIN OR EYES,

00:10:56.786 --> 00:10:58.956
BUT THIS GIVES ME NIGHTMARES.

00:10:58.956 --> 00:11:00.257
I NEED YOU TO BELIEVE THAT THIS

00:11:00.257 --> 00:11:02.125
THOUGHT TERRORIZES ME!

00:11:02.125 --> 00:11:03.160
I’M SCARED OF THE FACT THAT MY

00:11:03.160 --> 00:11:04.795
OWN DEATH MAY BE STARING ME IN

00:11:04.795 --> 00:11:05.896
THE FACE, AND I WON’T EVEN SEE

00:11:05.896 --> 00:11:06.930
IT COMING.

00:11:06.930 --> 00:11:09.199
THAT’S WHY I WANT MY HEAD.

00:11:09.199 --> 00:11:12.836
PLEASE TELL ME YOU BELIEVE THIS.

00:11:12.836 --> 00:11:14.137
&gt;&gt; I TOLD YOU.

00:11:14.137 --> 00:11:15.005
YOU’RE THE ONLY ONE I DO

00:11:15.005 --> 00:11:16.274
BELIEVE.

00:11:16.274 --> 00:11:17.341
THIS IS QUITE A CONUNDRUM.

00:11:17.341 --> 00:11:18.842
BOTH OF US ARE GETTING VERY

00:11:18.842 --> 00:11:20.278
UPSET BY SITUATIONS THAT ARE

00:11:20.278 --> 00:11:22.413
SIMPLY HYPOTHETICAL.

00:11:22.413 --> 00:11:26.317
&gt;&gt; YEAH, YOU’RE RIGHT.

00:11:26.317 --> 00:11:27.218
HEY, SHINRA...

00:11:27.218 --> 00:11:31.489
&gt;&gt; WHAT IS IT?

00:11:31.489 --> 00:11:33.324
&gt;&gt; I NEED TO HIT YOU.

00:11:33.324 --> 00:11:38.397
&gt;&gt; DO IT!

00:11:38.397 --> 00:11:39.931
ALL RIGHT, NOW I GET TO HIT

00:11:39.931 --> 00:11:42.201
YOU BACK.

00:11:52.277 --> 00:11:52.978
&gt;&gt; UH.

00:11:52.978 --> 00:11:53.846
&gt;&gt; PERFECT.

00:11:53.846 --> 00:11:54.847
YOU’RE PRETTIEST WHEN YOU’RE

00:11:54.847 --> 00:11:58.517
NOT HIDING YOUR FACE, YOU KNOW.

