&gt;&gt; [mutters]

00:12:36.557 --> 00:12:38.124
&gt;&gt; YO, IZAYA.

00:12:38.124 --> 00:12:40.127
&gt;&gt; DOTACHIN. BEEN AWHILE.

00:12:40.127 --> 00:12:41.528
&gt;&gt; WILL YA STOP CALLIN’ ME THAT?

00:12:41.528 --> 00:12:42.596
&gt;&gt; YEAH, ANYWAYS DO YOU KNOW

00:12:42.596 --> 00:12:43.897
WHERE THE NAME THE DOLLARS COMES

00:12:43.897 --> 00:12:45.299
FROM?

00:12:45.299 --> 00:12:46.300
&gt;&gt; ISN’T IT SOMETHIN’ LIKE,

00:12:46.300 --> 00:12:47.668
"GIMME ALL YOUR DOLLARS"?

00:12:47.668 --> 00:12:49.904
&gt;&gt; NO, NOT EVEN CLOSE.

