THEY JUST DAWDLE AROUND ALL DAY.

00:12:54.141 --> 00:12:56.010
BUT "DOLLARS" SOUNDS COOLER.

00:12:56.010 --> 00:12:57.612
&gt;&gt; DOTACHIN, TELL ME YOU SAW IT

00:12:57.612 --> 00:12:58.279
TOO!

00:12:58.279 --> 00:12:59.346
THE BLACK RIDER!

00:12:59.346 --> 00:13:00.347
&gt;&gt; I TOTALLY CAN’T BELIEVE THAT

00:13:00.347 --> 00:13:01.416
JUST HAPPENED.

00:13:01.416 --> 00:13:02.417
I DIDN’T HALLUCINATE ALL THAT

00:13:02.417 --> 00:13:03.551
CRAZINESS, DID I?

00:13:03.551 --> 00:13:05.387
IT WAS LIKE A CG CHARACTER OR

00:13:05.387 --> 00:13:06.120
SOMETHING.

00:13:06.120 --> 00:13:07.455
&gt;&gt; THAT CG CHARACTER IS ALSO

00:13:07.455 --> 00:13:08.923
PART OF THE DOLLARS.

00:13:08.923 --> 00:13:10.392
&gt;&gt; both: WHAT? WOW!

00:13:10.392 --> 00:13:11.193
&gt;&gt; IS THAT TRUE?

00:13:11.193 --> 00:13:12.027
&gt;&gt; both: THAT IS SO COOL!

00:13:12.027 --> 00:13:14.589
SO COOL. SO COOL.

00:13:18.033 --> 00:13:19.334
&gt;&gt; I’M A LITTLE SHOCKED BY ALL

00:13:19.334 --> 00:13:20.502
THIS.

00:13:20.502 --> 00:13:21.436
I KNEW THERE WERE A LOT OF

00:13:21.436 --> 00:13:22.570
PEOPLE ONLINE CLAIMING THAT

00:13:22.570 --> 00:13:23.572
THEY WERE MEMBERS OF THE

00:13:23.572 --> 00:13:24.707
DOLLARS.

00:13:24.707 --> 00:13:26.374
HOWEVER, I HAD NO IDEA SO MANY

00:13:26.374 --> 00:13:27.943
OF THEM WOULD ACTUALLY MAKE AN

00:13:27.943 --> 00:13:28.644
EFFORT TO TURN UP WHEN A

00:13:28.644 --> 00:13:30.579
MEETING WAS FINALLY CALLED.

00:13:30.579 --> 00:13:31.580
[laughs]

00:13:31.580 --> 00:13:33.949
HUMAN BEINGS DEFY IMAGINATION.

00:13:33.949 --> 00:13:35.584
REMEMBER, I KNOW YOU CAME HERE

00:13:35.584 --> 00:13:37.420
TO TOKYO HOPING TO ESCAPE THE

00:13:37.420 --> 00:13:39.455
HUMDRUM, BUT IN ABOUT SIX

00:13:39.455 --> 00:13:41.024
MONTHS, THIS’LL ALL SEEM

00:13:41.024 --> 00:13:42.591
PRETTY ORDINARY TO YOU.

00:13:42.591 --> 00:13:44.293
