00:13:44.293 --> 00:13:45.561
MOVE TO ANOTHER COUNTRY TO KEEP

00:13:45.561 --> 00:13:46.730
THINGS EXCITING OR START

00:13:46.730 --> 00:13:47.663
LOOKING FOR THINGS THAT ARE A

00:13:47.663 --> 00:13:50.466
LITTLE MORE UNDERGROUND.

00:13:50.466 --> 00:13:51.635
BUT I’D BE WILLING TO BET THAT

00:13:51.635 --> 00:13:54.203
YOU WOULD GET BORED OF THAT IN

00:13:54.203 --> 00:13:55.705
JUST A FEW DAYS AS WELL.

00:13:55.705 --> 00:13:56.973
&gt;&gt; [breathes angrily]

00:13:56.973 --> 00:13:58.308
&gt;&gt; THE ONLY WAY TO TRULY ESCAPE

00:13:58.308 --> 00:14:00.076
THE MUNDANE IS FOR YOU TO

00:14:00.076 --> 00:14:02.279
CONSTANTLY BE EVOLVING.

00:14:02.279 --> 00:14:03.747
WHETHER YOU CHOOSE TO AIM HIGH

00:14:03.747 --> 00:14:06.616
OR AIM LOW...

00:14:06.616 --> 00:14:08.752
ENJOY EACH DAY FOR WHAT IT IS.

00:14:08.752 --> 00:14:12.189
NOW, AS A SIGN OF RESPECT, I’VE

00:14:12.189 --> 00:14:13.758
DECIDED NOT TO CHARGE YOU FOR

00:14:13.758 --> 00:14:15.259
NAMIE YAGIRI’S PRIVATE CELL

00:14:15.259 --> 00:14:17.161
PHONE NUMBER, AND I’M NOT

00:14:17.161 --> 00:14:18.362
GONNA SELL YOU OUT ON BEING

00:14:18.362 --> 00:14:21.031
THE FOUNDER OF THE DOLLARS.

00:14:21.031 --> 00:14:22.767
IT’S YOUR ORGANIZATION.

00:14:22.767 --> 00:14:25.302
USE IT HOWEVER YOU CHOOSE.

00:14:30.007 --> 00:14:31.008
&gt;&gt; [whimpers]

00:14:31.008 --> 00:14:33.644
&gt;&gt; [growls] IZAYA!

00:14:33.644 --> 00:14:35.313
&gt;&gt; LOOKS LIKE IT’S TIME FOR ME

00:14:35.313 --> 00:14:36.681
TO GO.

00:14:36.681 --> 00:14:37.682
BEST OF LUCK TO YA,

00:14:37.682 --> 00:14:41.019
TARO TANAKA!

00:14:41.019 --> 00:14:42.788
&gt;&gt; GET BACK HERE, YOU BASTARD!

00:14:42.788 --> 00:14:45.423
IZAYA!

00:14:49.360 --> 00:14:51.497
&gt;&gt; WAS THAT...?

00:14:51.497 --> 00:14:53.164
[cries out]

00:14:53.164 --> 00:14:54.366
&gt;&gt; GET ’EM WHILE THEY’RE GOOD!

00:14:54.366 --> 00:14:55.701
&gt;&gt; AND THAT WAS IT.

