FOR THIS GUY...

00:15:00.038 --> 00:15:01.207
AND THAT GUY...

00:15:01.207 --> 00:15:02.741
AND FOR THE BOY.

00:15:02.741 --> 00:15:04.043
&gt;&gt; HEY, MIKADO.

