&gt;&gt; YOU’RE NOT MAKING ANY SENSE,

00:15:21.461 --> 00:15:22.795
YOU KNOW.

00:15:22.795 --> 00:15:24.797
&gt;&gt; AND EVEN FOR THOSE TWO.

