BUT WHENEVER I SEE YOUR FACE,

00:15:29.769 --> 00:15:31.838
I’M REMINDED OF THE PASSION

00:15:31.838 --> 00:15:33.773
AND LOVE I HAVE FOR HER.

00:15:33.773 --> 00:15:34.741
SO WITH THAT IN MIND, I’LL

00:15:34.741 --> 00:15:36.276
ACCEPT YOUR LOVE...

00:15:36.276 --> 00:15:38.178
UNTIL THE DAY I FINALLY GET HER

00:15:38.178 --> 00:15:40.047
BACK.

00:15:49.790 --> 00:15:50.724
&gt;&gt; HEY, GUYS.

