AFRAID I WON’T BE HERE LONG,

00:15:54.728 --> 00:15:56.830
I’M KINDA TIRED TONIGHT.

00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:57.698
&gt;&gt; WHAT, YOU PULL AN

00:15:57.698 --> 00:15:59.133
ALL-NIGHTER?

