HERE YET.

00:16:02.703 --> 00:16:05.206
&gt;&gt; WONDER IF KANRA WILL SHOW UP.

00:16:05.206 --> 00:16:06.841
&gt;&gt; HEY, SOMETHING JUST CAME UP.

00:16:06.841 --> 00:16:08.109
