AFTER THAT LITTLE ENTRANCE YOU

00:16:39.441 --> 00:16:41.677
MADE, I DOUBT ANYONE’S GONNA

00:16:41.677 --> 00:16:43.345
BE SCARED OF YOU ANYMORE.

00:16:43.345 --> 00:16:44.614
THINKING BACK, YOU DIDN’T KILL

00:16:44.614 --> 00:16:45.815
ANYONE, DID YOU?

00:16:45.815 --> 00:16:47.250
THAT SCYTHE ALL BARK AND NO

00:16:47.250 --> 00:16:47.883
BITE.

00:16:47.883 --> 00:16:49.185
I’M GUESSING YOU’RE GONNA GO

00:16:49.185 --> 00:16:50.686
AFTER THAT WOMAN NOW.

00:16:50.686 --> 00:16:51.721
I WOULD BE GLAD TO HELP YOU OUT

00:16:51.721 --> 00:16:53.156
WITH THAT.

00:16:53.156 --> 00:16:56.626
JUST CALL ME.

00:16:56.626 --> 00:16:58.261
BYE NOW.

00:16:58.261 --> 00:16:59.262
&gt;&gt; I HAVE NO IDEA WHERE

00:16:59.262 --> 00:17:01.231
NAMIE YAGIRI WENT.

00:17:01.231 --> 00:17:03.767
BUT I DON’T CARE. I’M ME...

00:17:03.767 --> 00:17:05.602
AND THAT’S ENOUGH.

00:17:05.602 --> 00:17:06.637
MY DAYS WERE ALWAYS PRETTY

00:17:06.637 --> 00:17:08.705
UNCOMPLICATED, NOT TOO FULL OF

00:17:08.705 --> 00:17:10.206
HOPE OR DESPAIR.

