HERE I AM, AND THERE YOU ARE.

00:17:20.217 --> 00:17:21.218
IF YOU CAN FIND REDEMPTION IN

00:17:21.218 --> 00:17:22.853
ME, THEN I CAN DO THE SAME

00:17:22.853 --> 00:17:28.592
WITH YOU.

