AND THE YOUNG BOY IS STILL

00:17:29.727 --> 00:17:31.428
PONDERING HIS CONVERSATION WITH

00:17:31.428 --> 00:17:33.798
IZAYA ORIHARA.

00:17:33.798 --> 00:17:34.899
CAN A PERSON TRULY HAVE A LIFE

00:17:34.899 --> 00:17:37.301
THAT’S ALWAYS NEW, ALWAYS FULL

