00:17:39.904 --> 00:17:40.905
OR IS IT JUST A MATTER OF TIME

00:17:40.905 --> 00:17:43.608
BEFORE THAT TOO BECOMES PART OF

00:17:43.608 --> 00:17:45.643
THE EVERYDAY?

