THAT’S MY SEAT!

00:17:57.690 --> 00:17:58.724
&gt;&gt; WELL, THERE’S A SPOT OPEN

00:17:58.724 --> 00:18:00.392
BEHIND THE CLASS REP.

00:18:00.392 --> 00:18:01.293
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:18:01.293 --> 00:18:02.928
WHO DO YOU THINK YOU ARE?

00:18:02.928 --> 00:18:04.530
YOU CAN’T JUST SHOW UP AND TAKE

00:18:04.530 --> 00:18:09.902
SOMEBODY’S SEAT.

00:18:09.902 --> 00:18:11.870
&gt;&gt; AS FOR HER, CHANCES ARE SHE

00:18:11.870 --> 00:18:12.971
WON’T BE SPENDING MUCH TIME

00:18:12.971 --> 00:18:15.241
WITH MIKA HARIMA ANYMORE.

00:18:15.241 --> 00:18:17.243
AND IN THE END, ONLY SHE WILL

00:18:17.243 --> 00:18:18.011
KNOW IF THAT’S THE RIGHT

00:18:18.011 --> 00:18:19.745
DECISION.

00:18:19.745 --> 00:18:21.981
BUT THEN, MAYBE SHE WON’T.

00:18:21.981 --> 00:18:23.316
IT’S RARE FOR A PERSON TO TRULY

00:18:23.316 --> 00:18:25.852
UNDERSTAND THEIR OWN HEART.

00:18:25.852 --> 00:18:27.520
AS SOMEONE ONCE SAID, THE

00:18:27.520 --> 00:18:29.789
BEST THING YOU CAN DO IS KEEP

00:18:29.789 --> 00:18:32.025
EVOLVING.

