BUT, UNFORTUNATELY, WHAT THE

00:18:38.765 --> 00:18:39.933
YOUNG BOY HAD FAILED TO ACCOUNT

00:18:39.933 --> 00:18:42.336
FOR WAS THE SHEER AMOUNT OF

00:18:42.336 --> 00:18:43.937
COURAGE IT WOULD TAKE IN ORDER

00:18:43.937 --> 00:18:45.272
FOR HIM TO ASK OUT HIS

00:18:45.272 --> 00:18:47.007
CLASSMATE.

