IN 30 SECONDS, THE BOY WILL

00:18:52.813 --> 00:18:54.448
FIND THE GIRL.

00:18:54.448 --> 00:18:56.651
IN 35 SECONDS, THE BOY WILL

00:18:56.651 --> 00:18:57.785
DISCOVER HIS BEST FRIEND

00:18:57.785 --> 00:18:59.820
HITTING ON THE GIRL.

00:18:59.820 --> 00:19:01.489
IN 45 SECONDS, THE BOY WILL

00:19:01.489 --> 00:19:04.292
KICK THE CRAP OUT OF HIM.

00:19:04.292 --> 00:19:05.993
IN 74 SECONDS, THE GIRL WILL

00:19:05.993 --> 00:19:07.528
REJECT THE BOY’S OFFER TO GET

00:19:07.528 --> 00:19:08.363
COFFEE.

00:19:08.363 --> 00:19:10.631
AND, IN 78 SECONDS, THAT GIRL

00:19:10.631 --> 00:19:11.832
WILL ASK THE BOY TO HAVE LUNCH

00:19:11.832 --> 00:19:14.069
WITH HER ON THE ROOF.

00:19:14.069 --> 00:19:15.503
HOW LONG WILL IT TAKE FOR HIM

00:19:15.503 --> 00:19:17.538
TO FALL IN LOVE WITH HER?

00:19:17.538 --> 00:19:19.074
AND HOW LONG BEFORE HE WORKS UP

00:19:19.074 --> 00:19:21.910
THE NERVE TO TELL HER?

00:19:21.910 --> 00:19:23.612
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:19:27.415 --> 00:19:28.784
&gt;&gt; I GOTTA SAY...

00:19:28.784 --> 00:19:32.988
THAT WAS VERY FOOLISH OF YOU.

00:19:32.988 --> 00:19:34.790
YOU THREW AWAY EVERYTHING FOR

00:19:34.790 --> 00:19:35.924
YOUR BROTHER’S TWISTED

00:19:35.924 --> 00:19:38.394
VERSION OF LOVE.

00:19:42.999 --> 00:19:46.668
[splash]

00:19:46.668 --> 00:19:48.838
OR MAYBE IT WAS YOUR TWISTED

00:19:48.838 --> 00:19:50.539
LOVE FOR YOUR BROTHER.

00:19:50.539 --> 00:19:52.742
SO THIS CAN’T LOOK GOOD, CAN IT?

00:19:52.742 --> 00:19:53.910
YOU’RE ABOUT TO MERGE WITH THE

00:19:53.910 --> 00:19:54.911
NEBRA PEOPLE.

00:19:54.911 --> 00:19:56.045
LET THEM CATCH WIND OF

00:19:56.045 --> 00:19:57.647
SOMETHING LIKE THIS, AND, THE

00:19:57.647 --> 00:19:58.948
NEXT THING YOU KNOW, YOU’VE GOT

00:19:58.948 --> 00:20:01.518
SOME MAFIA HIT-MAN ON YOUR TAIL.

00:20:01.518 --> 00:20:03.019
THEN AFTER THAT, POW!

00:20:03.019 --> 00:20:04.854
AND CHECKMATE.

00:20:04.854 --> 00:20:06.556
CLEANING CREW?

00:20:06.556 --> 00:20:07.124
&gt;&gt; THAT’S THEM.

00:20:07.124 --> 00:20:09.026
THAT’S THE NORMAL CREW THEY USE.

00:20:09.026 --> 00:20:11.428
&gt;&gt; GOT IT.

00:20:11.428 --> 00:20:13.797
[ringing]

00:20:13.797 --> 00:20:14.531
HELLO.

00:20:14.531 --> 00:20:15.398
THINGS ARE GETTING A LITTLE

00:20:15.398 --> 00:20:16.967
BIT HEATED IN YOUR NECK OF THE

00:20:16.967 --> 00:20:17.735
WOODS.

00:20:17.735 --> 00:20:18.702
YOU SHOULD GET OUT OF THERE

00:20:18.702 --> 00:20:22.372
SOON.

00:20:22.372 --> 00:20:23.807
I WISH THE KING PIECES COULD

00:20:23.807 --> 00:20:25.409
FIGHT EACH OTHER.

00:20:25.409 --> 00:20:27.911
THEY SHOULD CHANGE THAT RULE.

00:20:27.911 --> 00:20:28.879
I’VE GOTTA THINK THAT YOUR

00:20:28.879 --> 00:20:31.081
UNCLE WAS A LOT LIKE ME.

00:20:31.081 --> 00:20:32.783
HE QUESTIONED THE AFTERLIFE

00:20:32.783 --> 00:20:34.017
MORE THAN ANYONE...

00:20:34.017 --> 00:20:36.120
FEARED DEATH MORE THAN ANYONE...

00:20:36.120 --> 00:20:37.155
AND LONGED FOR HEAVEN MORE THAN

00:20:37.155 --> 00:20:38.756
ANYONE.

00:20:38.756 --> 00:20:40.758
BUT THE AFTERLIFE, WELL, THAT I

00:20:40.758 --> 00:20:42.126
BELIEVE IN

00:20:42.126 --> 00:20:44.863
WE’LL JUST LEAVE IT AT THAT.

00:20:44.863 --> 00:20:46.497
FOR WHATEVER REASON, DULLAHANS

00:20:46.497 --> 00:20:47.899
ARE ALWAYS DEPICTED AS WOMEN IN

00:20:47.899 --> 00:20:49.133
THE LEGENDS.

00:20:49.133 --> 00:20:51.002
DO YOU KNOW WHY THAT IS?

00:20:51.002 --> 00:20:52.003
&gt;&gt; NO, I DON’T.

00:20:52.003 --> 00:20:53.472
MY MEN DID A LITTLE RESEARCH ON

00:20:53.472 --> 00:20:54.839
THE MYTH, BUT, IN THE END, I

00:20:54.839 --> 00:20:56.841
THOUGHT IT WAS A WASTE OF TIME.

00:20:56.841 --> 00:20:58.009
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE ALWAYS THE PRAGMATIC

00:20:58.009 --> 00:20:58.910
ONE.

00:20:58.910 --> 00:21:00.979
WELL, SUIT YOURSELF.

00:21:00.979 --> 00:21:02.847
THERE’S A PLACE CALLED VALHALLA.

00:21:02.847 --> 00:21:04.950
IT’S SORT LIKE A HEAVEN.

00:21:04.950 --> 00:21:05.750
AND, ACCORDING TO NORDIC

00:21:05.750 --> 00:21:07.853
MYTHOLOGY, THE SOUL OF A FALLEN

00:21:07.853 --> 00:21:09.121
WARRIOR IS GUIDED TO VALHALLA

00:21:09.121 --> 00:21:10.589
BY AN ARMORED, FEMALE ANGEL

00:21:10.589 --> 00:21:12.892
KNOWN AS A VALKYRIE.

00:21:12.892 --> 00:21:14.594
A WOMAN WHO COMES TO GREET THE

00:21:14.594 --> 00:21:15.160
DEAD.

00:21:15.160 --> 00:21:18.030
DOESN’T THAT SOUND FAMILIAR?

00:21:18.030 --> 00:21:19.599
SOME THEORIZE THAT A DULLAHAN

00:21:19.599 --> 00:21:20.933
IS ACTUALLY A VALKYRIE WHO IS

00:21:20.933 --> 00:21:22.902
WANDERING AROUND ON EARTH.

00:21:22.902 --> 00:21:25.505
AND, IF THAT’S TRUE, THEN THIS

00:21:25.505 --> 00:21:27.573
HEAD IS PROBABLY WAITING...

00:21:27.573 --> 00:21:29.775
WAITING TO WAKE UP FOR WAR.

00:21:29.775 --> 00:21:31.044
THEN SHE CAN FIND HER WARRIOR

00:21:31.044 --> 00:21:33.179
AND TAKE HIM TO VALHALLA.

00:21:33.179 --> 00:21:34.948
THAT’S WHY SHE’S ALIVE, BUT WITH

00:21:34.948 --> 00:21:36.116
HER EYES CLOSED, BECAUSE WE

00:21:36.116 --> 00:21:37.984
AREN’T ON A BATTLEFIELD.

00:21:37.984 --> 00:21:40.020
IT’S MY WISH THAT SHE WOULD

00:21:40.020 --> 00:21:42.155
CHOOSE ME AS HER WARRIOR.

00:21:42.155 --> 00:21:43.690
IF THERE TRULY IS A VALHALLA

00:21:43.690 --> 00:21:45.091
AWAITING ME AFTER DEATH, HOW

00:21:45.091 --> 00:21:47.027
DO I EVEN PREPARE FOR THIS?

00:21:47.027 --> 00:21:48.094
I MEAN, I KNOW I’M NOT REALLY

00:21:48.094 --> 00:21:50.230
CUT OUT FOR BATTLEFIELD HEROICS.

00:21:50.230 --> 00:21:51.865
SO THEN I’LL HAVE TO START A

00:21:51.865 --> 00:21:54.968
WAR THAT ONLY I CAN WIN, RIGHT?

00:21:54.968 --> 00:21:55.969
[laughs]

00:21:55.969 --> 00:21:57.638
AREN’T I THE LUCKY ONE?

00:21:57.638 --> 00:21:58.972
IMAGINE ME, WHO DOESN’T BELIEVE

00:21:58.972 --> 00:22:00.074
IN A HEAVEN, MUCH LESS A

00:22:00.074 --> 00:22:01.842
VIRTUOUS LIFE.

00:22:01.842 --> 00:22:03.510
AND YET I STILL MEET AN ANGEL

00:22:03.510 --> 00:22:05.012
OF DEATH WHO’S FALLEN TO EARTH.

00:22:05.012 --> 00:22:06.213
&gt;&gt; WHATEVER.

00:22:06.213 --> 00:22:08.215
THAT’S SIMPLY A THEORY OF YOURS.

00:22:08.215 --> 00:22:09.917
&gt;&gt; WHOSOEVER BELIEVETH WILL BE

00:22:09.917 --> 00:22:10.618
SAVED.

00:22:10.618 --> 00:22:13.087
THIS IS JUST INSURANCE REALLY.

00:22:13.087 --> 00:22:14.656
EVEN IF I DO END UP IN A HELL

00:22:14.656 --> 00:22:16.858
SURROUNDED BY PAIN, AS LONG AS

00:22:16.858 --> 00:22:19.594
I COULD EXIST, I WOULDN’T CARE.

00:22:19.594 --> 00:22:21.963
BUT, THAT SAID, IF IT IS AT ALL

00:22:21.963 --> 00:22:23.498
POSSIBLE, I WOULD STILL PREFER

00:22:23.498 --> 00:22:24.499
HEAVEN.

00:22:24.499 --> 00:22:25.833
HEY, NAMIE.

00:22:25.833 --> 00:22:28.937
WHY DON’T WE ALL GO TO HEAVEN?

00:22:28.937 --> 00:22:30.572
AS A MEMBER OF THE DOLLARS, I’M

00:22:30.572 --> 00:22:32.540
GONNA KEEP THIS HIDING IN PLAIN

00:22:32.540 --> 00:22:33.776
SIGHT.

00:22:33.776 --> 00:22:35.010
THE LAST PLACE CELTY IS GOING

00:22:35.010 --> 00:22:36.278
TO LOOK FOR HER HEAD IS WITHIN

00:22:36.278 --> 00:22:37.980
THE SAME GANG THAT SHE BELONGS

00:22:37.980 --> 00:22:39.147
TO.

00:22:39.147 --> 00:22:40.048
I KNOW!

00:22:40.048 --> 00:22:41.249
YOU SHOULD BECOME PART OF THE

00:22:41.249 --> 00:22:42.551
DOLLARS TOO.

00:22:42.551 --> 00:22:44.019
IT’S A LITTLE KNOWN FACT THAT

00:22:44.019 --> 00:22:45.120
OUR BOSS DOESN’T TURN DOWN

00:22:45.120 --> 00:22:46.221
ANYONE.

00:22:46.221 --> 00:22:48.624
OF COURSE, AFTER A WHILE, I WAS

00:22:48.624 --> 00:22:50.025
THE ONE WHO WAS INSTRUMENTAL IN

00:22:50.025 --> 00:22:51.960
GATHERING PEOPLE.

00:22:51.960 --> 00:22:54.130
I SAY WE GIVE THIS FALLEN ANGEL

00:22:54.130 --> 00:22:57.133
A PAIR OF WINGS AGAIN.

00:22:57.133 --> 00:22:59.135
WHAT DO YA THINK?

00:22:59.135 --> 00:23:02.138
&gt;&gt; [singing in Japanese]

00:23:02.138 --> 00:23:10.179
♪ ♪

00:24:28.795 --> 00:24:30.997
&gt;&gt; IN HER DAILY LIFE, NOTHING

00:24:30.997 --> 00:24:33.277
EVER HAPPENS, NOTHING EVER

00:24:33.277 --> 00:24:35.811
CHANGES, EVEN THOUGH THINGS ARE

00:24:35.811 --> 00:24:37.444
BORN AND DISAPPEAR IN THE CITY

00:24:37.444 --> 00:24:39.277
EVERY SINGLE DAY.

00:24:39.277 --> 00:24:42.244
NEXT TIME, TAKES A SUDDEN TURN.

